JOHANNESBURG - eNCA's Moneyline runs a weekly feature in which well-known South Africans chat about their relationship with money.This week, we chatted with entrepreneur, Dr Richard Maponya."If you can manage to spend very little on luxuries and put away your money so that it accumulates. When it has accumulated you are able to do something about it," he said."I would advise people to know how to manage their budget. Once you can master that then you can become number one," he enthused.eNCA